* {{ill|Onsen Shrine|ja|温泉神社|12=draft}} - A {{ill|shrine|ja|神社|12=draft}} associated with {{ill|hot springs|ja|温泉|1=Onsen|1=Onsen|12=draft}}. * Shrines with the name "Onsen Shrine." ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōsaki)|ja|温泉神社 (大崎市)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōsaki|ja|大崎市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Miyagi Prefecture|ja|宮城県|12=draft}}, at {{ill|Naruko Onsen|ja|鳴子温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Yusen Shrine (Kōriyama)|ja|湯泉神社 (郡山市)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kōriyama|ja|郡山市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Fukushima Prefecture|ja|福島県|12=draft}}, at {{ill|Bandai-Atami Onsen|ja|磐梯熱海温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Iwaki)|ja|温泉神社 (いわき市)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Iwaki|ja|いわき市|12=draft}}, Fukushima Prefecture, at {{ill|Iwaki Yumoto Onsen|ja|いわき湯本温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōtawara)|ja|温泉神社 (大田原市中野内)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōtawara|ja|大田原市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Tochigi Prefecture|ja|栃木県|12=draft}}, at {{ill|Kurobane Onsen|ja|黒羽温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nasushiobara)|ja|温泉神社 (那須塩原市湯本塩原)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nasushiobara|ja|那須塩原市|12=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Shiobara Onsen|ja|塩原温泉郷|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Nasu Onsen Shrine|ja|那須温泉神社|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nasu|ja|那須町|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nasu District|ja|那須郡|12=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Nasu Onsen|ja|那須温泉郷|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nikkō)|ja|温泉神社 (日光市)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nikkō|ja|日光市|12=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Kinugawa Onsen|ja|鬼怒川温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|ja|温泉神社 (白浜町)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Shirahama|ja|白浜町|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nishimuro District|ja|西牟婁郡|12=draft}}, {{ill|Wakayama Prefecture|ja|和歌山県|12=draft}}, at {{ill|Nanki Shirahama Onsen|ja|南紀白浜温泉|12=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市)|12=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Unzen|ja|雲仙市|12=draft}}, {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県|12=draft}}, at {{ill|Unzen Onsen|ja|雲仙温泉|12=draft}}. There are over ten branch shrines with the same name on the {{ill|Shimabara Peninsula|