* {{ill|Onsen Shrine|ja|温泉神社|qq=draft}} - A {{ill|shrine|ja|神社|qq=draft}} associated with {{ill|hot springs|ja|温泉|1=Onsen|1=Onsen|qq=draft}}. * Shrines with the name "Onsen Shrine." ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōsaki)|ja|温泉神社 (大崎市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōsaki|ja|大崎市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Miyagi Prefecture|ja|宮城県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Naruko Onsen|ja|鳴子温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Yusen Shrine (Kōriyama)|ja|湯泉神社 (郡山市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Kōriyama|ja|郡山市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Fukushima Prefecture|ja|福島県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Bandai-Atami Onsen|ja|磐梯熱海温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Iwaki)|ja|温泉神社 (いわき市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Iwaki|ja|いわき市|qq=draft}}, Fukushima Prefecture, at {{ill|Iwaki Yumoto Onsen|ja|いわき湯本温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōtawara)|ja|温泉神社 (大田原市中野内)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Ōtawara|ja|大田原市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Tochigi Prefecture|ja|栃木県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Kurobane Onsen|ja|黒羽温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nasushiobara)|ja|温泉神社 (那須塩原市湯本塩原)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nasushiobara|ja|那須塩原市|qq=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Shiobara Onsen|ja|塩原温泉郷|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Nasu Onsen Shrine|ja|那須温泉神社|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nasu|ja|那須町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nasu District|ja|那須郡|qq=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Nasu Onsen|ja|那須温泉郷|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nikkō)|ja|温泉神社 (日光市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Nikkō|ja|日光市|qq=draft}}, Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Kinugawa Onsen|ja|鬼怒川温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|ja|温泉神社 (白浜町)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Shirahama|ja|白浜町|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nishimuro District|ja|西牟婁郡|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Wakayama Prefecture|ja|和歌山県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Nanki Shirahama Onsen|ja|南紀白浜温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Unzen|ja|雲仙市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Nagasaki Prefecture|ja|長崎県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Unzen Onsen|ja|雲仙温泉|qq=draft}}. There are over ten branch shrines with the same name on the {{ill|Shimabara Peninsula|ja|島原半島|qq=draft}}. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Kunimi)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市国見町多比良丁)|qq=draft}} - Located in Unzen, Kunimi-machi Tabirachō. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Azuma)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市吾妻町布江名)|qq=draft}} - Located in Unzen, Azuma-machi Fuenami. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Chijiwa)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市千々石町己)|qq=draft}} - Located in Unzen, Chijiwa-machi Mi. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Ariake)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市有家町山川)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Minamishimabara|ja|南島原市|qq=draft}}, Ariake-machi Yamakawa. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Kazusa)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市加津佐町己)|qq=draft}} - Located in Minamishimabara, Kazusa-machi Mi. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Yatsushiro)|ja|温泉神社 (八代市)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Yatsushiro|ja|八代市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Kumamoto Prefecture|ja|熊本県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Hinagu Onsen|ja|日奈久温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市青山町)|qq=draft}} - Located in {{ill|Beppu|ja|別府市|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Ōita Prefecture|ja|大分県|qq=draft}}, at {{ill|Beppu Onsen|ja|別府温泉|qq=draft}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu Tetsuwana)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市鉄輪)|qq=draft}} - Located in Beppu, at {{ill|Tetsuwana Onsen|ja|鉄輪温泉|qq=draft}}.
