uelle/Onsen Shrine (Nikkō)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Nikkō|Nikkō]], Tochigi Prefecture, at [[:en:Kinugawa Onsen|Kinugawa Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|ja|温泉神社 (白浜町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Shirahama, Wakayama|Shirahama]], [[:en:Nishimuro District, Wakayama|Nishimuro District]], [[:en:Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama Prefecture]], at [[:en:Nanki-Shirahama Onsen|Nanki Shirahama Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Unzen, Nagasaki|Unzen]], [[:en:Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki Prefecture]], at [[:en:Unzen Onsen|Unzen Onsen]]. There are over ten branch shrines with the same name on the [[:en:Shimabara Peninsula|Shimabara Peninsula]]. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Kunimi)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市国見町多比良丁)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Kunimi)|qq=}} - Located in Unzen, Kunimi-machi Tabirachō. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Azuma)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市吾妻町布江名)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Azuma)|qq=}} - Located in Unzen, Azuma-machi Fuenami. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Chijiwa)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市千々石町己)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Chijiwa)|qq=}} - Located in Unzen, Chijiwa-machi Mi. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Ariake)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市有家町山川)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Ariake)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Minamishimabara|Minamishimabara]], Ariake-machi Yamakawa. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Kazusa)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市加津佐町己)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Kazusa)|qq=}} - Located in Minamishimabara, Kazusa-machi Mi. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Yatsushiro)|ja|温泉神社 (八代市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Yatsushiro)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Yatsushiro|Yatsushiro]], [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]], at {{ill|Hinagu Onsen|ja|日奈久温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinagu Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市青山町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Beppu)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Beppu|Beppu]], [[:en:Ōita Prefecture|Ōita Prefecture]], at [[:en:Beppu Onsen|Beppu Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu Tetsuwana)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市鉄輪)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Beppu Tetsuwana)|qq=}} - Located in Beppu, at {{ill|Tetsuwana Onsen|ja|鉄輪温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tetsuwana Onsen|qq=}}.
