* {{ill|Onsen Shrines|lt=Onsen Shrines|lt=Onsen Shrine|ja|温泉神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine|qq=}} - A [[:en:Shinto shrine|shrine]] associated with [[:en:Onsen|Onsen]]. * Shrines with the name "Onsen Shrine." ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōsaki)|ja|温泉神社 (大崎市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Ōsaki)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Ōsaki, Miyagi|Ōsaki]], [[:en:Miyagi Prefecture|Miyagi Prefecture]], at {{ill|Naruko Onsen|ja|鳴子温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Naruko Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Yusen Shrine (Kōriyama)|ja|湯泉神社 (郡山市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yusen Shrine (Kōriyama)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Kōriyama|Kōriyama]], [[:en:Fukushima Prefecture|Fukushima Prefecture]], at {{ill|Bandai-Atami Onsen|ja|磐梯熱海温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bandai-Atami Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Iwaki)|ja|温泉神社 (いわき市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Iwaki)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Iwaki, Fukushima|Iwaki]], Fukushima Prefecture, at [[:en:Iwaki Yumoto Onsen|Iwaki Yumoto Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Ōtawara)|ja|温泉神社 (大田原市中野内)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Ōtawara)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Ōtawara|Ōtawara]], [[:en:Tochigi Prefecture|Tochigi Prefecture]], at {{ill|Kurobane Onsen|ja|黒羽温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kurobane Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nasushiobara)|ja|温泉神社 (那須塩原市湯本塩原)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Nasushiobara)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Nasushiobara|Nasushiobara]], Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Shiobara Onsen|ja|塩原温泉郷|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shiobara Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Nasu Onsen Shrine|ja|那須温泉神社|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nasu Onsen Shrine|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Nasu, Tochigi|Nasu]], [[:en:Nasu District, Tochigi|Nasu District]], Tochigi Prefecture, at {{ill|Nasu Onsen|ja|那須温泉郷|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nasu Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Nikkō)|ja|温泉神社 (日光市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Nikkō)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Nikkō|Nikkō]], Tochigi Prefecture, at [[:en:Kinugawa Onsen|Kinugawa Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|ja|温泉神社 (白浜町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Shirahama)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Shirahama, Wakayama|Shirahama]], [[:en:Nishimuro District, Wakayama|Nishimuro District]], [[:en:Wakayama Prefecture|Wakayama Prefecture]], at [[:en:Nanki-Shirahama Onsen|Nanki Shirahama Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Unzen, Nagasaki|Unzen]], [[:en:Nagasaki Prefecture|Nagasaki Prefecture]], at [[:en:Unzen Onsen|Unzen Onsen]]. There are over ten branch shrines with the same name on the [[:en:Shimabara Peninsula|Shimabara Peninsula]]. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Kunimi)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市国見町多比良丁)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Kunimi)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Unzen, Kunimi-machi Tabirachō. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Azuma)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市吾妻町布江名)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Azuma)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Unzen, Azuma-machi Fuenami. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Unzen Chijiwa)|ja|温泉神社 (雲仙市千々石町己)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Unzen Chijiwa)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Unzen, Chijiwa-machi Mi. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Ariake)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市有家町山川)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Ariake)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Minamishimabara|Minamishimabara]], Ariake-machi Yamakawa. *** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Kazusa)|ja|温泉神社 (南島原市加津佐町己)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Minamishimabara Kazusa)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in Minamishimabara, Kazusa-machi Mi. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Yatsushiro)|ja|温泉神社 (八代市)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Yatsushiro)|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} - Located in [[:en:Yatsushiro|Yatsushiro]], [[:en:Kumamoto Prefecture|Kumamoto Prefecture]], at {{ill|Hinagu Onsen|ja|日奈久温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinagu Onsen|qq=}}. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市青山町)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Beppu)|qq=}} - Located in [[:en:Beppu|Beppu]], [[:en:Ōita Prefecture|Ōita Prefecture]], at [[:en:Beppu Onsen|Beppu Onsen]]. ** {{ill|Onsen Shrine (Beppu Tetsuwana)|ja|温泉神社 (別府市鉄輪)|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Onsen Shrine (Beppu Tetsuwana)|qq=}} - Located in Beppu, at {{ill|Tetsuwana Onsen|ja|鉄輪温泉|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tetsuwana Onsen|qq=}}.
